    "body" : "<p>Use this website:</p>\n\n<p><code>https://besticon-demo.herokuapp.com/allicons.json?url=www.stackoverflow.com</code></p>\n\n<p>It will find all logos for a website in multiple sizes and return a nice json string with meta data including the url to the icon.  You simply replace <code>www.stackoverflow.com</code> with your domain.</p>\n\n<p>The site also has a gui for entering in websites manually if you prefer:</p>\n\n<pre><code>https://besticon-demo.herokuapp.com/\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Here is a sample string returned from querying for the stack overflow website:</p>\n\n<pre><code>{\n   \"url\":\"www.stackoverflow.com\",\n   \"icons\":[\n      {\n         \"url\":\"http://stackoverflow.com/apple-touch-icon.png\",\n         \"width\":158,\n         \"height\":158,\n         \"format\":\"png\",\n         \"bytes\":3445,\n         \"error\":null,\n         \"sha1sum\":\"c78bd457575a3221c6b3d0d17ffb00ffc63d7cd0\"\n      },\n      {\n         \"url\":\"http://cdn.sstatic.net/Sites/stackoverflow/img/favicon.ico?v=4f32ecc8f43d\",\n         \"width\":32,\n         \"height\":32,\n         \"format\":\"ico\",\n         \"bytes\":5430,\n         \"error\":null,\n         \"sha1sum\":\"4f32ecc8f43d0986b9c6ce9f37999e86c0b829ef\"\n      },\n      {\n         \"url\":\"http://stackoverflow.com/favicon.ico\",\n         \"width\":32,\n         \"height\":32,\n         \"format\":\"ico\",\n         \"bytes\":5430,\n         \"error\":null,\n         \"sha1sum\":\"4f32ecc8f43d0986b9c6ce9f37999e86c0b829ef\"\n      }\n   ]\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
