    "body" : "<p><strong>This method can be used to get Favicon Icon bitmap</strong></p>\n\n<pre><code> private Bitmap fetchFavicon(Uri uri) {\n        final Uri iconUri = uri.buildUpon().path(\"favicon.ico\").build();\n        Log.i(TAG, \"Fetching favicon from: \" + iconUri);\n\n        InputStream is = null;\n        BufferedInputStream bis = null;\n        try\n        {\n            URLConnection conn = new URL(iconUri.toString()).openConnection();\n            conn.connect();\n            is = conn.getInputStream();\n            bis = new BufferedInputStream(is, 8192);\n            return BitmapFactory.decodeStream(bis);\n        } catch (IOException e) {\n            Log.w(TAG, \"Failed to fetch favicon from \" + iconUri, e);\n            return null;\n        }\n    }\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
