    "body" : "<p>I know I am late but this API will help others</p>\n<p>Android doesn't support favicon files natively, you can fetch favicon in different ways but can't show/use it.</p>\n<p>Google provides free API to get favicon in image format.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?sz=64&amp;domain_url=microsoft.com\" rel=\"noreferrer\">https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?sz=64&amp;domain_url=microsoft.com</a></p>\n<p>Use Picasso to show fetched favicon in an image view.</p>\n"
